Text.string: You think you can play with the big kids?
Someone will be right with you.
Never gonna make it in this industry.
Don't call us, we'll call you.
That's why you're stuck in middle management!
No bonus for my tech guys!
If you're not at the table, you're on the menu!
Guess I'm getting my hands dirty!
Below my pay grade, but fine!
All right, I'll get down in the trenches.
If you want something done right...
If the soldiers can't cut it, the general steps in!
The weak fall to the strong.
Do you know who I am?
Not a straight shooter, are you?
